identifier
_____

it is userdefiend word.
THis word is used to name of variable,methodame,classname,....
rule
____
(1)
it consist of 
a to z
A to Z
0 to 9
_

$
(2)not start with digit

(3)space not allow

(4)case senistive

(5)reserved word not allow



53 reserved word 
 
 3   literal  true false null
50  keyword

48  used keyword     if else for while ,.....
2    unused keyword    goto const





